<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - 괌세이브카드</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --max-width: 1240px;
            --primary-color: #4FC3F7;
            --secondary-color: #667eea;
            --accent-color: #87CEEB;
            --text-dark: #333;
            --text-light: #666;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: "Noto Sans KR", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #87CEEB 0%, #4FC3F7 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .hero-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 15px 40px;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .travel-icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .travel-icon {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        /* Desktop styles */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .hero-section {
                padding: 60px 20px 80px;
            }
            
            .travel-icons {
                gap: 30px;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            
            .travel-icon {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
        }
        
        .travel-icon:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        .travel-icon:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1s; }
        .travel-icon:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }
        .travel-icon:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 2s; }
        .travel-icon:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 2.5s; }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }
        
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            font-family: 'Arial Black', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.4;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }
        
        /* Desktop styles */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 4rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                letter-spacing: 8px;
            }
            
            .hero-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
                padding: 0;
            }
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .btn-hero {
            background: white;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 8px 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-height: 44px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 280px;
        }
        
        .cta-buttons .btn {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            margin: 8px 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid white;
            min-height: 44px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 280px;
        }
        
        /* Desktop styles */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .feature-card {
                border-radius: 20px;
                padding: 30px;
                margin: 20px 0;
                box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            }
            
            .feature-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
            
            .feature-icon {
                font-size: 3rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            
            .btn-hero {
                border-radius: 50px;
                padding: 15px 40px;
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                margin: 10px;
                width: auto;
            }
            
            .cta-buttons .btn {
                padding: 15px 30px;
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                border-radius: 50px;
                margin: 10px;
                width: auto;
            }
        }
        
        .cta-buttons .btn-primary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-color: white;
            color: white;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .cta-buttons .btn-primary:hover {
            background: white;
            color: #4FC3F7;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .cta-buttons .btn-outline-light {
            background: transparent;
            border-color: white;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-buttons .btn-outline-light:hover {
            background: white;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .stats-section {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            color: white;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .banner-section {
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .banner-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .banner-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .banner-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            border-color: #4FC3F7;
        }
        
        .banner-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .banner-card:hover .banner-image {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        .banner-content {
            padding: 20px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .banner-name {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        
        .banner-description {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
        
        .banner-action {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: auto;
            padding-top: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
            }
            
            .hero-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            .travel-icons {
                gap: 20px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            
            .travel-icon {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .banner-image {
                max-height: 100px;
            }
            
            .feature-card {
                margin: 10px 0;
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .cta-buttons {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center; /* 가운데 정렬 */
                gap: 12px;
            }
            .cta-buttons .btn {
                display: block;
                width: 90%;            /* 동일한 가로폭 */
                max-width: 340px;     /* 최대폭 제한으로 일관성 */
                margin: 0 auto;       /* 좌우 동일 여백 */
            }
            
            .banner-image {
                height: 160px;
            }
            
            .banner-content {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            .banner-name {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
        }
        
        /* 제휴업체 신청 배너 스타일 */
        .partner-application-banner {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .partner-banner-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .partner-banner-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-partner-apply {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-partner-apply:hover {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            border-color: white;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 네비게이션 포함 -->
    <%- include('partials/mobile-nav') %>
    <%- include('partials/desktop-nav') %>
    <div class="container" style="max-width: var(--max-width);">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="hero-section">
            <!-- Travel Icons Row -->
            <div class="travel-icons">
                <div class="travel-icon"><i class="fas fa-plane"></i></div>
                <div class="travel-icon"><i class="fas fa-suitcase-rolling"></i></div>
                <div class="travel-icon"><i class="fas fa-fish"></i></div>
                <div class="travel-icon"><i class="fas fa-shopping-bag"></i></div>
                <div class="travel-icon"><i class="fas fa-palm-tree"></i></div>
                <div class="travel-icon"><i class="fas fa-sailboat"></i></div>
            </div>
            
            <% if (partnerAgency) { %>
                <!-- 제휴 여행사 로고만 표시 -->
                <div class="partner-branding mb-3">
                    <% if (partnerAgency.logo_url) { %>
                        <img src="<%= partnerAgency.logo_url %>" alt="<%= partnerAgency.name %> 로고" 
                             style="max-height: 80px; margin-bottom: 20px;" class="partner-logo">
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <h1 class="hero-title">
                GUAM SAVE CARD
                <% if (partnerAgency) { %>
                    <small class="text-light opacity-75 d-block" style="font-size: 0.5em; margin-top: 10px;">
                        (<%= partnerAgency.name %>)
                    </small>
                <% } %>
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">괌 여행 필수품, 단 하나의 QR로 30만원 이상의 혜택을!</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="<% if (partnerAgency) { %>/register?agency=<%= partnerAgency.code %><% } else { %>/register<% } %>" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg me-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-credit-card me-2"></i>할인카드 발급받기
                </a>
                <a href="<% if (partnerAgency) { %>/login?agency=<%= partnerAgency.code %><% } else { %>/login<% } %>" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg me-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-id-card me-2"></i>내 카드 보기
                </a>
                <a href="<% if (partnerAgency) { %>/stores?agency=<%= partnerAgency.code %><% } else { %>/stores<% } %>" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg me-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-store me-2"></i>제휴업체 보기
                </a>
                <a href="#features" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>자세히 알아보기
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <div id="features" class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>💰 무료로 받는 30만원+ 혜택</h4>
                    <p>제휴 매장에서만 받을 수 있는 독점 할인<br>쇼핑, 레스토랑, 투어, 교통까지 실속 있는 혜택<br>카드 한 장으로 여행 경비를 확 줄여드립니다</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>📲 초간편 발급 & 사용</h4>
                    <p>발급비 무료 – 신청 즉시 QR 카드 발급<br>QR 스캔 한 번으로 즉시 할인 적용<br>복잡한 쿠폰, 번거로운 바우처는 이제 안녕!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-globe-asia"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>🌏 괌 여행의 필수 아이템</h4>
                    <p><strong>한국인 관광객 1,000명+</strong>이 이미 사용<br>5,000건 이상의 할인 적용으로 검증된 만족도<br>괌을 즐기는 똑똑한 방법, 이제 선택이 아닌 필수</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats Section -->
        <div class="stats-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">50+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">제휴 매장</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">98%</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">사용자 만족도</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">억단위</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">누적 혜택 절감</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">1000+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">한국인 관광객</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Banner Section -->
        <% if (typeof banners !== 'undefined' && banners && banners.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="banner-section">
            <div class="row">
                <% banners.forEach(function(banner) { %>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 banner-item">
                        <div class="banner-card" data-link="<%= banner.link_url || '' %>" onclick="trackBannerClick(<%= banner.id %>, this.dataset.link)">
                            <img class="banner-image" src="<%= banner.image_url %>" alt="<%= banner.advertiser_name %>">
                            <div class="banner-content">
                                <div class="banner-name"><%= banner.title || banner.advertiser_name %></div>
                                <% if (banner.description) { %>
                                    <div class="banner-description"><%= banner.description %></div>
                                <% } %>
                                <div class="banner-action">
                                    <span>자세히 보기</span>
                                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ms-2"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <!-- Success Stories Section -->
        <div class="success-stories-section mb-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 text-center mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-white mb-3">🎆 사용자 후기 & 성공 사례</h3>
                    <p class="text-white opacity-75">실제 사용자들의 생생한 후기를 확인해보세요</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="feature-card text-center">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-quote-left" style="color: #4FC3F7;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mb-3">"가족 4명이 3박 4일 괌 여행에서 <strong>25만원 절약</strong>했어요! 레스토랑, 쇼핑몰에서 엄청난 할인 받았습니다."</p>
                        <small class="text-muted">- 김★★ 고객 (서울)</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="feature-card text-center">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-quote-left" style="color: #4FC3F7;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mb-3">"신혼여행에서 사용했는데 <strong>호텔 레스토랑부터 쇼핑까지</strong> 모든 곳에서 할인이 되더라고요. 정말 편리해요!"</p>
                        <small class="text-muted">- 박★★ 고객 (부산)</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="feature-card text-center">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-quote-left" style="color: #4FC3F7;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mb-3">"친구들과 같이 갔는데 <strong>QR 하나로 모든 곳에서 할인</strong>이 되니까 너무 신기하고 편해요. 다음에도 꼭 사용할거예요!"</p>
                        <small class="text-muted">- 이★★ 고객 (대구)</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h3 class="text-white mb-4">🚀 지금 바로 발급하세요!</h3>
            <p class="text-white mb-4 opacity-90">👉 무료 발급으로 괌 전역에서 VIP처럼 할인 혜택을 누리세요.</p>
            <a href="<% if (partnerAgency) { %>/register?agency=<%= partnerAgency.code %><% } else { %>/register<% } %>" class="btn btn-hero btn-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-rocket me-2"></i>무료 발급 시작하기
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer 제휴업체 신청 배너 -->
        <div class="partner-application-banner mt-5 mb-4">
            <div class="partner-banner-card" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#partnerApplicationModal">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-store me-2"></i>한국인 관광객에게 매장을 알리고 혜택을 제공하세요
                        </h4>
                        <p class="mb-1">괌세이브카드에 입점하면 매출이 달라집니다.</p>
                        <small class="text-light">Promote your store to Korean tourists and increase your sales.<br>Join Guam Save Card and see the difference in your business.</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 text-end">
                        <button class="btn btn-partner-apply">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake me-2"></i>Apply for Partnership
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 제휴업체 신청 모달 -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="partnerApplicationModal" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-handshake me-2"></i>제휴업체 신청
                    </h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <h6 class="text-primary">괌세이브카드와 함께 성장할 비즈니스 파트너를 찾고 있습니다</h6>
                        <small class="text-muted">We are looking for business partners to grow with Guam Save Card</small>
                    </div>
                    
                    <form id="partnerApplicationForm">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">
                                    <i class="fas fa-store me-2"></i>업체명 / Business Name *
                                </label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="business_name" required 
                                       placeholder="예: ABC Restaurant">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">
