                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i>이메일 / Email *
                            </label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" required 
                                   placeholder="예: contact@business.com">
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-phone me-2"></i>전화번호 / Phone *
                            </label>
                            <input type="tel" class="form-control" name="phone" required 
                                   placeholder="예: +1-671-123-4567">
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="alert alert-info">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
                            신청서 접수 후 담당자가 직접 연락드리겠습니다.<br>
